narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It is an interesting class on the diaspora in Nigeria. The weekly reading responses were not too hard to keep up with.

Nigeria and Its Diaspora is an interesting course for students to take in order to gain an understanding of the country of Nigeria and the way that Nigeria culture is expressed and understood throughout the world.
